 &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">Looking out on the Kyoto landscape from the City Viewing Platform at Okochi Sanso Villa on Mt. Ogura. Mt. Hiei can be seen in the center of the photograph. 嵐山の丘にある大河内山荘の市内展望台から京都を眺める。写真の中央には比叡山が見ます。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02601-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02601-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Evening at Kiyomizu・清水の夕べ</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211111/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Evening at Kiyomizu・清水の夕べ" /><published>2021-11-11T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-11-11T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kiyomizu</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211111/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
