 &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">Beautiful clouds at sunset, looking at the city of Kyoto from Kiyomizudera temple. 清水寺から京都の街を眺めた夕暮れ時の美しい雲。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02514.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02514.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Cloud &amp;amp; Boat・雲とボート</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211110/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Cloud &amp;amp; Boat・雲とボート" /><published>2021-11-10T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-11-10T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/cloud</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211110/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
