Above &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nison-in&quot; targe=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Nison-in Temple&lt;/a&gt; on Mt. Ogura, this is said to have been the site of a villa belonging to &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fujiwara_no_Teika&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Fujiwara no Teika&lt;/a&gt;, the poet who compiled the famous anthology ”&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ogura_Hyakunin_Isshu&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;One Hundred Poems by One Hundred Poets&lt;/a&gt;,“ in the 13th century. This peaceful site looks out onto the Kitasaga area of Arashiyama.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
    小倉山にあるこの場所は、13世紀に「&lt;a href=&quot;https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E9%A6%96&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;小倉百人一首&lt;/a&gt;」の歌人である&lt;a href=&quot;https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%97%A4%E5%8E%9F%E5%AE%9A%E5%AE%B6&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;藤原定家&lt;/a&gt;の別荘があった場所と言われています。
 &lt;/p&gt;
 
 &lt;div class=&quot;subimagegroup&quot;&gt;
     &lt;div class=&quot;subimage&quot;&gt;
         &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02157.jpg&quot;/&gt;   
     &lt;/div&gt;   
     &lt;div class=&quot;subimage&quot;&gt;
         &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02111-HDR.jpg&quot;/&gt;  
     &lt;/div&gt;   
     &lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">Above Nison-in Temple on Mt. Ogura, this is said to have been the site of a villa belonging to Fujiwara no Teika, the poet who compiled the famous anthology ”One Hundred Poems by One Hundred Poets,“ in the 13th century. This peaceful site looks out onto the Kitasaga area of Arashiyama. 小倉山にあるこの場所は、13世紀に「小倉百人一首」の歌人である藤原定家の別荘があった場所と言われています。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02150-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02150-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Shisendo・詩仙堂</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211105/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Shisendo・詩仙堂" /><published>2021-11-05T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-11-05T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/shisendo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211105/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
