&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
         1641年に建てられた詩仙堂の「詩仙の間」から見た美しい庭園。
 &lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Gardens" /><summary type="html">Beautiful garden viewed from the main room of Shisendo, built in 1641. 1641年に建てられた詩仙堂の「詩仙の間」から見た美しい庭園。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02074.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2111_A7R02074.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Tenryuji Garden・天龍寺の庭園</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211104/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Tenryuji Garden・天龍寺の庭園" /><published>2021-11-04T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-11-04T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tenryuji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211104/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
